data.description: Welcome to one of the most desirable neighborhoods in Chesapeake VA Wellington Woods. This beautiful 3,480sq ft. home Is a must see! located in a Cul-de -Sac. Featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms and an attached 2 car garage, a huge backyard with a wooded view and a deck; Great for entertaining. This freshly painted home has lots of natural light. Open floor plan and cathedral ceilings. A very spacious eat in kitchen with center island, pantry and plenty of counter space opens to the family room and sunroom, with open views of the formal living and dining room. The giant primary suite features a garden tub, separate shower, double vanity, a walk-In closet & sitting area. The spacious first floor bedroom has access to a full bathroom and has access to the exterior of the home.  2 patio areas, a basketball goal with paved court area & huge storage shed. No HOA fees! Nearby shopping, entertainment & easy Interstate access!
